%A9tape%2C%20la%20collectivit%C3%A9%20re%C3%A7oit%20des%20propositions%20personnalis%C3%A9es%20d%27ing%C3%A9nierie%2C%20%20de%20financement%20ou%20d%27accompagnement%20par%20des%20services%20experts%20de%20la%20th%C3%A9matique%20projet.%20Chaque%20blocage%20fait%20l%27objet%20de%20recommandations%20pour%20arriver%20%C3%A0%20la%20concr%C3%A9tisation%20du%20projet%20et%20son%20%C3%A9valuation%20d%27impact.%0A%0A%23%23%20Strat%C3%A9gie%0A%0A-%20Se%20positionner%20en%20tant%20que%20point%20d%27entr%C3%A9e%20des%20projets%20des%20collectivit%C3%A9s%20territoriales%0A%0A-%20Equiper%20les%20plans%20et%20programmes%20ANCT%20pour%20avoir%20des%20prescripteurs%20unissant%20collectivit%C3%A9s%20et%20l%27Etat%20Local%0A%0A-%20S%27int%C3%A9grer%20dans%20l%27%C3%A9cosyst%C3%A8me%20gr%C3%A2ce%20%C3%A0%20la%20promesse%20du%20%22Dites-le%20nous%20une%20fois%22.%20Une%20information%20%3D%201%20seule%20saisie%20en%20se%20synchronisant%20avec%20d%27autres%20services%20cl%C3%A9s%20%28D%C3%A9marches%20simplifi%C3%A9es%2C%20Grist%2C%20Aides%20Territoires%2C...%29%0A%0A-%20Retrouver%20les%20853%20CRTE%20%C3%A0%20un%20seul%20endroit.%20Soit%20plus%20de%2040%20000%20projets%20%C3%A0%20accompagner%20%28ing%C3%A9nierie%2C%20financement%20et%20ambition%20%C3%A9cologique%29%0A%0AObjectifs%2030%20juin%0A%0A-%20D%C3%A9ploiement%20progressif%20du%20guichet%20unique%20dans%20au%20moins%20un%20d%C3%A9partement%20par%20r%C3%A9gion%20%0A-%20Int%C3%A9gration%20de%20l%27ensemble%20des%2078.000%20projets%20des%20CRTE%20%28Contrats%20de%20r%C3%A9ussite%20de%20la%20Transition%20Ecologique%29%20de%20France%2C%20ouverture%20aux%20intercommunalit%C3%A9s.%0A-%20Interconnexion%20avec%20D%C3%A9marche%20Num%C3%A9rique%20%3A%20pr%C3%A9-remplissage%20d%E2%80%99une%20partie%20du%20formulaire%20de%20demande%20de%20subvention%20Fonds%20Vert%202026%20et%20des%20dossiers%20DTER%2FDSIL.%0A%20%0A%0AObjectifs%2031%20d%C3%A9cembre%20%0A%0A-%20Int%C3%A9gration%20%C3%A0%20Aides-territoires%20pour%20fluidifier%20le%20parcours%2